criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  an IQ score below 70;

          -  a chronological age between 18 and 44 years;

          -  a receptive vocabulary score at or above five years of age;

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  previous diagnosis of any chronic or co-morbid condition that could affect the
             performance of the target exercise tasks as assessed by the AHA/ACSM Health/Fitness
             Facility Preparticipation Screening Questionnaire (ACSM, 2014);

          -  a record of currently being pregnant or undergoing hormonal replacement or cancer
             therapy;

          -  prior or current experience with a similar intervention.
